Dialogue: 1,0:23:04.57,0:23:11.62,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}世界居然 如此娟丽
Dialogue: 1,0:23:11.70,0:23:15.29,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}喜欢你 说不出口
